						               													<description>Life is bustling within the castle walls. But you want for more. You want for a life in the Keep. Unfortunately, so does everyone else.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;KEEP is a card drafting game where you compete to gain enough wealth to rise up from your humble station and start a life beyond the walls of the keep. Each round, you&amp;rsquo;ll choose a card from the central commons, or from a hand of cards that is passed to your neighbor after each turn. There are multiple types of items to choose from that vary in their value, as well as characters that can be played for their ability or selected for end of game scoring. Be the player with the most coins at the end of the game and you&amp;rsquo;ll be able to start a new life in the keep.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Key Points&amp;#10;- Fast card drafting game that plays 2 to 5 players in 30 minutes or less!&amp;#10;- Humorous themes and uniquely styled artwork.&amp;#10;- Use a combination of public and private drafting to collect what you need each round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
